QuestData.Title: The Unmaker
QuestData.Description: Argus is Sargeras' solution for existence; an end to all things. For everyone that might ever live, bring an end to the Unmaker.
QuestData.LogDescription: Defeat Argus the Unmaker in Antorus, the Burning Throne.

Objectives.Objective: Defeat Argus the Unmaker in the Antorus, The Burning Throne
